sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Phone as 📱 Phone App
    participant RBI as 🏛️ RBI Server
    participant Bank as 🏦 User's Bank
    participant Watch as ⌚ Smartwatch
    
    User->>Phone: Opens ZiPPaY App
    User->>Phone: Selects Amount: ₹500
    Phone->>Phone: Stores amount in State
    
    User->>Phone: Confirms via Biometric
    Phone->>Phone: Validates Fingerprint ✓
    
    Phone->>Phone: Requests OTP (2FA)
    Phone->>User: Displays OTP Prompt
    User->>Phone: Enters OTP from Email
    Phone->>Phone: Validates OTP ✓
    
    Phone->>RBI: POST /api/v1/wallet/load
    Note over Phone,RBI: Encrypted Request: {amount: 500, user_id, device_id}
    
    RBI->>Bank: Verify Account Balance
    Bank->>Bank: Check Account ₹10,000 ✓
    Bank-->>RBI: Balance Sufficient ✓
    
    RBI->>RBI: Generate e-Rupee Token
    Note over RBI: Token: {TokenID, Amount, Timestamp, Nonce}
    
    RBI->>RBI: Create ECDSA Signature
    RBI->>RBI: Encrypt with Watch Public Key (AES-256)
    
    RBI-->>Phone: Return Encrypted Token + Signature
    Note over RBI,Phone: TLS 1.3 Encrypted Response
    
    Phone->>Watch: Initiate BLE Handshake
    Phone->>Watch: Authenticate Device Certificate
    Watch->>Watch: Verify Phone Certificate ✓
    
    Phone->>Watch: Send Encrypted e-Rupee Token via BLE
    Note over Phone,Watch: BLE ECDH Encrypted Channel
    
    Watch->>Watch: Receive & Decrypt Token (Private Key in SE)
    Watch->>Watch: Verify RBI Signature ✓
    Watch->>Watch: Store Token in Secure Element
    Watch->>Watch: Update Balance: ₹0 → ₹500
    
    Watch->>Watch: Record Transaction in LocalLedger
    Note over Watch: TX_LOAD_001: {amount: 500, source: RBI, timestamp}
    
    Watch-->>Phone: Send Confirmation: ✓ Loaded
    Phone->>Phone: Update UI: "Balance: ₹500"
    Phone-->>User: Display Success Message ✓
    
    Watch-->>User: Display on Screen: "✓ ₹500 Loaded"
    Watch->>Watch: Play Success Tone (ascending 3-note beep)
    Watch->>Watch: Haptic Feedback: 100ms pulse
    
    Note over User,Watch: Watch is now OFFLINE-CAPABLE
    Note over User,Watch: Can make 5 NFC payments before sync required
